{"tid":945614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"母親鼓勵下自製降傘跳樓 烏克蘭15歲少年身亡","createTime":"2018-12-18T04:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:52:41.000Z","uid":131548,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1adafbf93ed18ff9749bc7ed8404e3abf3965bc","tid":945614,"uid":131548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭東部城市馬克耶夫卡日前發生一幕荒唐的悲劇。15歲少年菲爾索夫（Bogdan Firsov），近日帶着自製降落傘，來到大概43米高的14層樓頂樓，想來個高空跳傘炫耀一下，但不幸降落傘並未能成功打開，最後他背部撞擊地面當場死亡。據悉，他的母親與親友當時也在現場，其母親甚至在兒子跳樓前還在樓下鼓勵他跳。<br />\n<br />\n從影片中可見，菲爾索夫站在烏克蘭東部城市馬克耶夫卡（Makiivka）的一棟建築物頂層。他張開雙臂，縱身一躍從約43米高的樓頂跳下，身後可以看到拖着降落傘，不幸的是，降落傘沒有打開，菲爾索夫直接摔在地上當場身亡。<br />\n<br />\n一名目擊者表示：「有一群人在那邊，沒人試圖阻止少年，他們只是在一旁拍影片，根本沒常識。」他補充稱，自己親眼看到少年的背部撞地，場面令他相當難受。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，菲爾索夫的母親與其他親戚也在場，一共10多人，他們鼓勵少年跳下，目的似乎是為了拍攝影片在社交網絡上炫耀。菲爾索夫墜地後，他的母親對於兒子的死亡感到十分震驚，一時間拒絕離開現場。還有目擊者提到，少年墜落前先在屋頂上待了約兩分鐘，雖然他戴着安全帽，地上也有墊子，但他墜落後仍不幸當場身亡。<br />\n<br />\n有專家表示，即使降落傘打開了也救不了菲爾索夫的命，因為跳傘所需的最低高度大約是70米，大約相當於25層高的建築。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1390620/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1390620%2F&d=80JSO3C4DhQkSCqIxZi%2BV%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=7a685652\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1390620%2F&h=97faab7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1390620/</a><br />\n<br />\nCls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25db1c0e8c0fec2605085c238bc4cf76eae93e27","tid":945614,"uid":131548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"成班望撚住佢跳樓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb23ea8f702487ae7ff3da10e939282bef9d0c1","tid":945614,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為跳傘所需的最低高度大約是70米，大約相當於25層高的建築。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a48a4a2292f620bcebb2b2fc859669b3bd2a5b","tid":945614,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"低空傘工作高度都請緊一二百米起,佢都係想死ja"},{"pid":"6ce4e3251051945cf22a628809ef10cd99647220","tid":945614,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvJXj1j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvJXj1j.gif&h=15810950&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}